RWE Agrees Sale of German Grid Amprion, Handelsblatt Reports

-- B y   B r i a n   P a r k i n
-- 
2011-07-14T06:45:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-14/rwe-agrees-sale-of-german-grid-amprion-handelsblatt-reports.html
RWE AG (RWE)  agreed a majority sale of its
Amprion German power grid to a group of investors led by
 Commerzbank AG (CBK) ,  Handelsblatt  reported, citing no one.  The sale price of the unit is more than 1 billion euros
($1.4 billion) including debt, the newspaper said without being
more specific. RWE will keep a 25 percent stake in the network,
it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brian Parkin in Berlin at 
 bparkin@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
